name: Miller
description: My name is Miller, i am a soldier and i have been working with the American government for some couple of years as a military man.. I am a man with good sense of humor, a man who has the fear of God.. I am looking for a woman who can help me build a home(family), a woman with good potentials, a woman that has the fear of God, a woman that will respect me as her husband as i am willing and ready to respect her as my darling wife… I hope i find a perfect woman that can raise a God fearing family with/for me…
